        "sanitize": false,
        "show": null,
        "text": "<p>A permit is not required for a tank that will be on site no more than 180 days, total. The tank must be installed in compliance with all codes and standards, and the manufacturer&rsquo;s requirements. State Department of Environmental Protection Siting Approval is required for a tank that will be on a site for 4 months or more. Contact DEP Directly at (207) 287-7688 if you have a tank that requires DEP Siting Approval, but not a Fire Marshal&rsquo;s Office permit.</p>\n<p></p>",
